    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I think that&#39;s EXACTLY what home cooking is! It&#39;s comforting and brings your family together, while not consuming all of your time. </p>
<p>On the other hand, it&#39;s also what makes holiday meals so memorable. You spend hours, even DAYS,  preparing something special for your family.  </p>
