    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>YES!  There is beauty in simple meals, although I would argue that meals do not really have to have beauty to be something you enjoy.  All the attention we give to cooking is great, but truly we can appreciate that it still &#8220;counts&#8221; to make a grilled cheese at home instead of a fancier, more labor intensive meal.  You&#39;re at home.  You&#39;re cooking.  It&#39;s great.</p>
