    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="http://everybodylikessandwiches.com" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">kickpleat</a></cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2014/10/even-on-a-good-day/#comment-42234"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2014-10-25T17:33:38-04:00">Saturday, October 25, 2014 at 5:33 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Love this post, Molly. To me, cooking has never  been about putting on a big production. It&#39;s about getting tasty food into our mouths relatively quickly and easily and healthily. As for this soup, I&#39;ll be making it soon. Thanks 🙂 </p>
    </div>

