    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I&#39;m like that, too &#8211; I&#39;m too tired to cook huge meals all the time, esp since we all work at home so it is 3 (!!!) meals a day. I get it. YES. Now, onto this soup &#8211; super yum. LOVE it. and i have everything I need to make it. Usually we make that sort of thing with pumpkin and curry &#8211; this will be a lovely change. </p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
