    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Thanks for keeping it real, as always, Molly. I love that you have full life and that regardless of that, you still cook at home.  It doesn&#39;t matter if they are simple, it is still cooking and it still counts and it is beyond better than microwaving a frozen dinner. I wouldn&#39;t be able to balance half of the things I would want to include in my life if I made a bigger more involved meal, every day.  </p>
