      <p>What a revelation.</p>
<p>My husband and I have this discussion nearly once a week along with my own internal dialogue.</p>
<p>While we both like to cook and cook well, the reality is that we do it about 3 times a week. It causes us (well&#8230;me) such angst that we don&#39;t cook daily. It&#39;s long past time to ease up. So thanks.</p>
