    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>A meal is a meal is a meal. The point is in the sharing, I believe. Thanks for your words and your recipes &#8211; they feed us.</p>
<p>Also, do you have a theory on what type of dog Alice is? She looks the perfect little grey mongrel. I want five of her, haha.</p>
